trans-unit.source: Provides a standard set of navigation-related commands.
trans-unit.target: 提供一組標準的功能相關的命令。

trans-unit.source: The NavigationCommands class exposes a standard set of navigation-related commands, including browser and document navigation.
trans-unit.target: NavigationCommands 類別會公開一組標準的瀏覽的相關命令，包括瀏覽器和文件的導覽。

trans-unit.source: For more information on commands and commanding, see [Commanding Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 如需有關命令和命令的詳細資訊，請參閱[指揮概觀](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)。

trans-unit.source: Gets the value that represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Browse Back" name="Browse Back" href=""></xref> command.
trans-unit.target: 取得值，表示<xref uid="langword_csharp_Browse Back" name="Browse Back" href=""></xref>命令。

trans-unit.source: This command indicates the intention to navigate back to the previous page in the journal.
trans-unit.target: 這個命令表示向後巡覽至日誌中的上一頁。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> implement support for responding to the BrowseBack, although you are not required to use it; in many cases the implementation in response to that command is the responsibility of the application writer.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>和<xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>實作支援 BrowseBack 回應，雖然您不需要直接使用; 在許多情況下該命令的回應中的實作是應用程式寫入器的責任。</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow></xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>

trans-unit.source: This command indicates the intention to navigate forward the next page in the journal.
trans-unit.target: 這個命令表示要往前巡覽日誌中的下一個頁面。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> implement support for responding to the BrowseForward command, although you are not required to use it; in many cases the implementation in response to that command is the responsibility of the application writer.

trans-unit.source: This command indicates the intention to navigate home.
trans-unit.target: 此命令表示要瀏覽首頁。

trans-unit.source: There is no implementation for responding to the BrowseHome command on any given [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] class.
trans-unit.target: 沒有回應 BrowseHome 命令，在任何給定的實作[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]類別。

trans-unit.source: As such, you need to provide an appropriate implementation, which is shown in the example.
trans-unit.target: 因此，您需要提供適當的實作，範例所示。
